Package com.arkavquarium.item

Class Food

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.arkavquarium.AquariumObject
      • com.arkavquarium.item.Item
        • com.arkavquarium.item.Food

  • public class Food
extends Item
    Represents food that is given to the Guppy

    Food is destroyed when it touches the bottom of the aquarium.

    It inherits the Item class

    Version:
    1.1
    Author:
    Adylan Roaffa
    See Also:
    Guppy, Item
